Decommercialization is a broad term. It refers to the general concept of moving
away from profit-driven practices to ones that are more socially responsible.
For this project, we are looking at a vision of total decommercialization. 

## Total decommercialization
A vision where the gathering has no connection to the capitalistic system at
all. There is no expectation of reciprocity.

## Partial decommercialization
A vision where the gathering

To what extent can gatherings be hosted under total decommercialization in our
society?

## Something special happens when there is no money involved
For example workaway.